{"word":"εἰσαφικνέομαι","slug":"εἰσαφικνέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰσαφικνέομαι</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>ἐς-απικνέομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-αφίξομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-αφικόμην</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:— <i>to come into</i> or <i>to, reach</i> or <i>arrive at</i> a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>ἐσαπ. ἐς τόπον</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}